{"tid":424152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同仆街親戚食飯 點算","createTime":"2017-10-04T12:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T07:03:00.000Z","uid":151429,"like":3,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5e493cb7a0dc12ccec3825109f07b49097921f05","tid":424152,"uid":151429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"呢個親戚 本身係香港人 上咗大陸做生意<br />\n本身份人就好撚仆街 又不負責任<br />\n又拖我哋屋企錢又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無啦啦上嚟黐中秋飯食<br />\n一個大男人成40歲 <br />\n已經係屋企樓下 講曬幾多樓 樓下密碼幾多號 <br />\n話唔撚識上嚟要搵人湊佢上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我聽到電話即刻落去 <br />\n落到去又畀佢屌話我行得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係喺架𨋢到當住五六個人面前屌<br />\n<br />\n食緊飯又喺度食煙 話支煙冇煙油就當住成枱人係咁噴<br />\n但係其實就好撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話要食魚咪夾畀佢囉 又話細嚿又話要豆醬<br />\n根本成程飯就冇食過嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗住唔理佢就算啦<br />\n食完飯抹枱又話我掃曬啲嘢落地下 但係根本就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫我食月餅 我都未應佢 <br />\n佢懶搞笑眨兩下眼 然後成撚個月餅車落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家仲話要喺屋企瞓 加菲貓？<br />\n大家有咩方法可以整鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5573f914fa4620d504684f5616142e1cf06aad84","tid":424152,"uid":106149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"打鳩佢啦"},{"pid":"db1a27c6c7cbc5fc91280a65e303fd12216b83c4","tid":424152,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"夜晚開電視嘈佢 同佢講唔滿意就返屋企訓"},{"pid":"ef1d38a5da425a15bfbcf3668e7a110b7c00647c","tid":424152,"uid":151429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夜晚開電視嘈佢 同佢講唔滿意就返屋企訓</blockquote><br />\n有諗過大聲播Metal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe